{"tid":1615521,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"押注港府放棄聯滙！巴斯：本港經濟將嚴重下滑    呼籲沽港元轉揸美元","createTime":"2019-10-03T06:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T06:51:45.000Z","uid":35790,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4a0abced46e19276a4f46fecdb99c63ac263f49d","tid":1615521,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:23:49.000Z","msg":"【資本外流】押注港府放棄聯滙！巴斯：本港經濟將嚴重下滑<br />\n<br />\n本港示威活動持續，經濟活動受到影響，有對沖基金經理更押注本港聯繫滙率將會被打破。對沖基金Hayman Capital Management 創辦人Kyle Bass（巴斯）在阿姆斯特丹出席會議時表示，香港經濟面臨嚴重下滑，社會動盪將會刺激資本外流，推高利率，並迫本港放棄三十多年的聯繫滙率政策。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，由於反政府示威活動，本港經濟下滑將會耗盡流動資金，預期本港9月及10月份的外滙儲備數字將會惡化，並將在接下來的12至18個月內，有大量資本及投資資金外流，香港經濟將會是一個「巨大的問號」。<br />\n<br />\n對於中資公司到美國上市，他認為，在美國集資的中國公司應該受到更嚴格的審查，而他本人永遠不會投資於中國的網絡巨頭公司。<br />\n<br />\nKyle Bass正管理專注於香港的對沖基金，於金融危機期間，他在美國次貸危機中沽空成名，他在三年前揚言重倉沽空港元及人民幣，但無功而還，<span style=\"color: red;\">今年亦曾多次呼籲沽港元轉揸美元。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191003/60111833\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191003%2F60111833&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGBD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=9ee73719\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191003%2F60111833&h=c269e85b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191003/60111833</a>"},{"pid":"02f059862c28d4ba44ee28407824534b0b3a5515","tid":1615521,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:29:56.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"6f0b9144b094618e77f87c2a12a295cdf746eddd","tid":1615521,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:30:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"eed8a196c9cc3c2e065464732214bc34d99ad65f","tid":1615521,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:31:31.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"c79cad161b57d0bda8a8db567928430d12b7433a","tid":1615521,"uid":438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:32:34.000Z","msg":"今個月出糧都未得閒換美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d727d6e1532e0909f0e1d8793e4fefd309177a3","tid":1615521,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:34:00.000Z","msg":"01 傳聞將公佈&quot;緊急法&quot;及&quot;蒙面法&quot;<br />\n資金唔外流才怪"},{"pid":"ae23c30e1db0dbf2c0c80aa7f487cbd6a2730802","tid":1615521,"uid":104582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:34:18.000Z","msg":"反正我一出糧就換哂做美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2674d6b8ec70c950a5db993b9701e1269c5fb28","tid":1615521,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:35:43.000Z","msg":"唔好咁興奮，有留意開會知道kyle bass呢排成日講嘢唔中<br />\n唔知佢係專登出口術定真係估錯"},{"pid":"1521bc9ebe9468c5bddd931edc85dd3a96028b77","tid":1615521,"uid":59910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:37:30.000Z","msg":"搵個真係賺到錢嘅黎講野好唔好，俾d 說服力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4a120dd893b8cd6295af9b4f4eaece0cec498a","tid":1615521,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:44:50.000Z","msg":"你成日諗住佢爆 佢就唔爆<br />\n到你覺得佢唔會爆 佢就開始爆"},{"pid":"2f6a3e83e79f1037f969696a95d3584d493204c2","tid":1615521,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />靜靜地"}]}